<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="value-vt">value <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'væljuː/    美 /'væljuː/  </p>
<p>[不用于进行时态]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>评价；估价：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>How do you <strong>value</strong> him <strong>as</strong> a writer?
他作为作家，你如何评价他？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>valued</strong> the painting <strong>at</strong> $2,000. 
他给这幅画估价2000美元。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>重视；珍惜：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We should value what we have and try our best to overcome any difficulty in life.
我们应该珍惜我们所拥有的，并尽最大努力克服生活中的困难。</p><footer>2008 湖南书面表达</footer></div></div>